description: The impressive inner wall of the keep casts long shadows across the grassy sward.  A couple kiosks and multi-colored tents have been spread out thru the area away from the great wall.  Small groups of militia sporadically wander the area near the wall keeping watch over the merchants and the occasional shopper.

The impressive inner wall of the keep casts deep shadows across the moonlit grassy sward.  A couple kiosks and multi-colored tents have been spread out thru the area away from the great wall.  Small groups of militia sporadically wander the area near the wall keeping watch over the merchants and the occasional shopper.
title: [Guardian Keep, Inner Wall]
